cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_ConfigurationIndex to an out-of-range value (999) will cause invalid PRACH configuration and random access failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_ConfigurationIndex 設定為超出範圍的值 (999)，會導致無效的 PRACH 配置，並造成隨機接入失敗。
